<headline>LSI Logic Corp Q1 earnings summary.</headline>
<text>
<p>MILPITAS, Calif., April 15 (Reuter)</p>
<p>				1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr primary     $0.29		    $0.32</p>
<p> Shr diluted     0.28		     0.31</p>
