<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE - Fully diluted earnings per share are based on average common and common equivalent shares outstanding.  In computing fully diluted earnings per share for the periods presented, net income is increased for interest (net of tax effect) on the convertible debentures ($1,279,000 and $1,524,000 for the three month periods ended March 31, 1997 and 1996, respectively) considered dilutive common stock equivalents.</p>
